metadata.name: Terra
metadata.description:
PLANET is a space that truly belongs to adventurers, and everything begins here

Each PLANET has its own unique ecosystem. Players can build their own houses on these planets, form guilds, kill unique monsters, and collect precious resources

Each planet of PLANET is unique and fully controlled by players. Players can expand their territory and compete with other players through purchasing, trading and exploring

In PLANET, every exploration and battle will have new surprises waiting for players. Players can obtain NFTs by killing monsters, or dig precious resources on the planet. As the game progresses, players can upgrade and expand their houses, obtain more powerful weapons and equipment, and form guilds with other players to explore this wonderful metaverse together

PLANET serves as a carrier, which gives players the opportunity to own their own metaverse land and build their own kingdom on this planet. It will bring endless fun and challenges to players.
